item.title: recently
item.description: 19:00 Tuesday 30 May 2017 JST Been wonderfully busy with Marble Track 3. Bought a new camera which I plan to use for stop action photos, but before setting it up, I needed to make an extension to my desk so the camera would be far enough away to take photos properly. I made three towers made of three sticks each, each stick made of two pairs of bamboo chopsticks, unsplit.
